<strong>Studio Album, released in 1975</strong><br><br>

<strong>Songs / Tracks Listing</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">1. Une nuit à Paris (8:38) :<br>- One Night in Paris (2:25)<br>- The Same Night in Paris (2:52)<br>- Later the Same Night in Paris (3:21)<br>2. I'm Not in Love (6:08)<br>3. Blackmail (4:32)<br>4. The Second Sitting for the Last Supper (4:30)<br>5. Brand New Day (4:05)<br>6. Flying Junk (4:15)<br>7. Life Is a Minestrone (4:46)<br>8. The Film of My Love (5:08)<br><br>Total Time 42:02<br><br>Bonus tracks on 1997 remaster:<br>9. Channel Swimmer (2:56)<br>10. Good News (3:50)</p>

<strong>Line-up / Musicians</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">- Eric Stewart / lead electric & steel (1,3) guitars, piano (3,4,6), electric piano (2,4,6), organ (4,8), vocals (2,4-6 lead), mixing<br>- Lol Creme / electric & acoustic (6) guitars, piano (1,2,4-8), organ (3), violin & Moog & Fx (5), autharp (6), electric piano (7), vibes (1), percussion (1,4,7,8), mandolin (8), vocals (7-lead)<br>- Graham Gouldman / 4- & 6-string (6) basses, double bass (5), acoustic (6,7) & electric guitars, autoharp (6), mandolin (8), percussion (1), vocals (8-lead)<br>- Kevin Godley / drums & percussion, timpani (1,5), Moog (2), marimba & bass drum & cello (5), timbales (7), bongos (8), vocals (5-lead)</p>

<strong>Releases information</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">
Artwork: Hipgnosis with Humphrey Ocean (drawing)<br><br>LP Mercury &#8206;- 6310 500  (1975, UK)<br><br>CD Mercury &#8206;- 830 776-2   (1990, US)<br>CD Mercury &#8206;- 532 964-2  (1997, UK) Remastered by  Roger Wake with 2 bonus tracks
</p>


